{"tid":2013576,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"沙中綫最終報告：港鐵禮頓須對管理及監管嚴重失誤負責","createTime":"2020-05-12T11:22:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-12T19:21:22.000Z","uid":70063,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"67ff5609a42e10f715f7b6d24fd967dc1650fc5f","tid":2013576,"uid":70063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:22:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=390759\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390759&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmAVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=db53ffcd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D390759&h=ce820371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=390759</a><br />\n<br />\n港鐵沙中綫被揭發工程質量問題以及遺失大量檢測，政府公開獨立調查委員會最終報告，指港鐵及承建商禮頓須對管理及監管嚴重失誤負責，政府作為監督者亦有責任。<br />\n<br />\n報告又指，紅磡站擴建工程在採取適當措施後，可安全及適合作預定用途，相關措施料年中全部完成。"},{"pid":"0761ef61b557d7a41f72135815dd87ff4fa92bcf","tid":2013576,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"適當措施=放置play幾個月，扮冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2312e3e2ad9852411613736aa5a9223ff86139a0","tid":2013576,"uid":235152,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:34:10.000Z","msg":"同中科講差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"763db73eafbc71d0eba703b1e69ff04781ac5230","tid":2013576,"uid":311412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0761ef61b557d7a41f72135815dd87ff4fa92bcf","tid":2013576,"uid":346806,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"適當措施=放置play幾個月，扮冇野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-12T19:21:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.coi-hh.gov.hk/pdf/COI_Final_Report_Chi.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.coi-hh.gov.hk%2Fpdf%2FCOI_Final_Report_Chi.pdf&d=EvsgW2mpOVZdTd1tTx%2BWmAVY%2FuVTJuRH1wmMvp6vMc0%3D&h=93ce8a2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.coi-hh.gov.hk/pdf/COI_Final_Report_Chi.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">[size=5]//297. 有關適當措施分為四個類別，概述如下：<br />\n<br />\na. 就螺絲帽組件的問題，建議在 A 區帽樑與東西走廊層板連接的某些位置進行工程 (加裝鋼筋及加厚個別層板 )，工程範圍長約 6 5 米 。<br />\n<br />\nb. 有見於抗剪箍筋造工欠佳，建議加強 抗剪箍筋、加厚個別層板／牆板，以及／或增加承重牆和支 柱等。擬議工程範圍不超 過 A 區 、 B 區 、 C 區和香港體育館區總樓面面積的2.5%。委員會明白，適當措施現僅限於 A 區的東西走廊層板及南北走廊層板。<br />\n<br />\nc. 關於東西走廊層板與連續牆 之間的施工接縫位置，建議在B 區 和 C 區的東面連續牆加裝鋼筋，工程範圍長約 6 0 米 。<br />\n<br />\nd. 至於滲水位置，建議進行灌漿或其他預防滲水措施。//[/size=2]</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n唔明..................."}]}